<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refund Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Add your custom styles -->
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
        <p>We strive to ensure customer satisfaction. If you are not satisfied with your order, please review our refund policy.</p>

        <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>Refunds are available if the product is damaged or not as described. Refunds are not provided for change of mind.</p>

        <h2>2. Requesting a Refund</h2>
        <p>To request a refund, please contact us within 24 hours of receiving your order. Provide your order details and reason for the request.</p>

        <h2>3. Processing Refunds</h2>
        <p>Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days. The amount will be credited back to your original payment method.</p>

        <h2>4. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding refunds, please contact us.</p>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
